d (Javascript changes).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>v1.0.4</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> User Capabilities</li>\r\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Alert message before resetting all settings</li>\r\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Added nonce checks to save, delete single, delete bulk & duplicate</li>\r\n<li><strong>Added:</strong> Plugin will now conditionally load scripts only when slider is used</li>\r\n<li><strong>Changed:</strong> Removed Ajax from delete, bulk delete and duplicate. Plugin no longer Ajax dependent</li>\r\n<li><strong>CSS:</strong> Added CSS properties to riva.slider.pro.css for iframe</li>\r\n<li><strong>CSS:</strong> IE7 fixes added to main CSS file & IE7 file removed</li>\r\n<li><strong>CSS:</strong> IE classes added to admin area for IE7, IE8, IE9</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Shadow URL when using \'Custom\' styling & Multi-site</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Serial code will now get removed if invalid & using Multi-site</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Dimensions error when using Custom Styling with no shadow image</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Global settings not saving for some users</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Error checking to update-check.php file incase wp_remote_post fails (due to SSL or other)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Major changes to how riva_slider_pro_file_content works</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Youtube rel attribute</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Validated riva_slider_pro_image() in functions.php</li>\r\n</ul>\";}}','yes'),(487,0,'riva_slider_pro_dynamic_css','e22f177113a227115a5b14077dbd88a7','yes'),(713,0,'webninja_ga_options','a:22:{s:16:\"internal_domains\";s:21:\"libertybellmoving.com\";s:10:\"account_id\";s:11:\"UA-XXXXXX-X\";s:14:\"enable_tracker\";b:1;s:15:\"track_adm_pages\";b:0;s:12:\"ignore_users\";b:1;s:14:\"max_user_level\";i:8;s:13:\"footer_hooked\";b:0;s:14:\"filter_content\";b:1;s:15:\"filter_comments\";b:1;s:22:\"filter_comment_authors\";b:1;s:15:\"track_ext_