they were in before the move.\r\n</div>','Long Movers','','publish','closed','closed','','long-distance-movers','','','2012-02-04 17:33:00','2012-02-04 17:33:00','',0,'http://andybeckmann.biz/host/lbm/public_html/lbm/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),(20,1,'2011-12-15 17:04:46','2011-12-15 17:04:46','<h3 class=\"top\">Moving your Piano is easy with our Piano Movers!</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hometext\">\r\n<a href=\"http://libertybellmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/piano_moving.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://libertybellmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/piano_moving.jpeg\" alt=\"SmallPiano\" title=\"long_haul_moves\" width=\"150\" height=\"152\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-119\" /></a>From the smallest Spinets to the largest Grand Piano, piano moving performed by Liberty Bell Moving offers homeowners peace of mind knowing their piano is being moved by trained piano movers.\r\n\r\nOur trained and registered Maine piano movers and piano tuners take pride in the careful disassembly padding, strapping, shipping and reassembly of your piano. Contact us today about our Piano Moving Services!\r\n\r\n<h3>Trust Liberty Bell Moving with your Piano Move Today!</h3>\r\n\r\nFrom the smallest Spinets to the largest Grand Piano, piano moving performed by Liberty Bell Moving offers homeowners peace of mind knowing their piano is being moved by trained piano movers.\r\n\r\nOur trained and registered Maine piano movers and piano tuners take pride in the careful disassembly padding, strapping, shipping and reassembly of your piano.\r\n\r\n<h3>Liberty Bell Moving has the experience and equipment to handle:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>moving spinet pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving console pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving player pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving studio pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving upright pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving baby grand pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving full grand pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving concert grand piano</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nIf you have us move and tune your piano, we recommend that the piano should be acclimated to the home for 3-4 weeks before scheduling a date for a piano tuning by our Registered Piano Technician.\r\n\r\n<h3>Piano Information</h3>\r\n\r\nBesides the fact that piano is heavy – it is also bulky and has an uneven distribution of weight. With that comes inertia and problems with balancing when you try to maneuver it, especially when moving the piano in a narrow passage. Professional piano movers know that the piano is extremely sensitive to a shock because it has a very delicate inner mechanism.\r\n\r\nThe iron frame, also called the “plate”, sits atop the soundboard, and serves as the primary bulwark against the force of string tension (in a modern grand the total string tension can approach 20 tons). The frame is made of cast iron and if it cracks the damage is irreparable.\r\n\r\nNo matter how much care we put into moving your piano, we always recommend having it tuned post move. Pianos are knocked out of tune very easily. If a perfect pitch is a priority, consider having our registered piano tuner bring the original sound back into your Piano.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Small Spinet piano or console piano weigh about 300-500 pounds</li>\r\n<li>Full size upright piano (also called Russian Piano) weighs about 700 pound or more</li>\r\n<li>Baby Grand piano, grand piano or parlor pianos – can weigh up to 1300 pounds</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Piano Movers','','publish','closed','closed','','piano-movers','','','2012-02-04 16:30:30','2012-02-04 16:30:30','',0,'http://andybeckmann.biz/host/lbm/public_html/lbm/?page_id=20',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2011-12-15 17:05:03','2011-12-15 17:05:03','<h3 class=\"top\">Packing Services just don\'t get any better!</h3>\r\n<div class=\"hometext\">\r\n\r\nWondering where to get moving boxes? Look no further. Liberty Bell Moving and Storgae will deliver boxes to your residence. Just call our office and place an order.\r\n\r\nA well packed home can be moved more safely and efficiently. If you choose to pack yourself 