nvaluable in keeping your goods secure and intact during the trip. At Liberty Bell Moving, our professionals make every effort to keep your possessions in the exact condition they were in before the move.\r\n</div>','Long Movers','','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-5','','','2012-01-17 20:26:22','2012-01-17 20:26:22','',18,'http://libertybellmoving.com/18-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(399,1,'2012-01-17 20:26:26','2012-01-17 20:26:26','<h3 class=\"top\">Local Moving</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hometext\">\r\nFrom the city apartments moves of Portland, ME, Lewiston, ME Portsmouth NH, to the spacious suburban residential moves in Waterford, ME, Portland, ME, Laconia, NH areas, our friendly and courteous local movers can be found assisting our customers with timely and cost effective moving services and moving supplies all over Central, Southern and Northern Maine and New Hampshire.\r\n\r\nOur multiple locations allow us to dispatch Maine movers and New Hampshire movers who will be closest to you, minimizing drive time costs and allowing us to provide a targeted start time for your moving services. Our local movers in New England and branch offices also ensure a crew familiar with your town and neighborhood.\r\n\r\n<h3>Locations throughout Maine</h3>\r\n\r\nWe have offices throughout central and southern Maine. We are primarily a Portland Maine moving company and provide moving services in Cape Elizabeth, Freeport, Cumberland, South Portland, Scarborough and all over Maine. We have Movers in Saco Maine who are well versed in serving the Biddeford, Saco, Old Orchard and all of Southern Maine region. Our 20,000 square ft. warehouse provides heated storage and movers in Gorham Maine areas that branch out to Standish, Limington, Hiram and into York county. Liberty Bell Movings Raymond location serves all of the lakes region and gets our movers in Gray Maine, Lewiston, Auburn, Naples and Sebago Maine. Our Waterford Maine movers covers the bridgtonBethel, Harrison, Lovell, South Paris regions. We also service all of New Hampshire from our Portsmouth and Laconia New Hampshire offices.\r\n\r\nWe serve the following cities and towns among others: South Portland, Kennebunkport, Portland, Cumberland, Saco, Biddeford, Scarborough, Raymond, Lewiston, Auburn, Windham, Westbrook, Freeport, Waterford, Bridgton, Gorham, Norway, Gray, Portsmouth, Laconia, Manchester, Conway, Ossipee and everything in between!\r\n\r\n</div>','Local Movers','','inherit','open','open','','16-revision-4','','','2012-01-17 20:26:26','2012-01-17 20:26:26','',16,'http://libertybellmoving.com/16-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(400,1,'2012-01-17 20:26:11','2012-01-17 20:26:11','<h3 class=\"top\">Moving your Piano is easy with our Piano Movers!</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hometext\">\r\n<a href=\"http://libertybellmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/piano_moving.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://libertybellmoving.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/piano_moving.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"long_haul_moves\" width=\"150\" height=\"152\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-119\" /></a>From the smallest Spinets to the largest Grand Piano, piano moving performed by Liberty Bell Moving offers homeowners peace of mind knowing their piano is being moved by trained piano movers.\r\n\r\nOur trained and registered Maine piano movers and piano tuners take pride in the careful disassembly padding, strapping, shipping and reassembly of your piano. Contact us today about our Piano Moving Services!\r\n\r\n<h3>Trust Liberty Bell Moving with your Piano Move Today!</h3>\r\n\r\nFrom the smallest Spinets to the largest Grand Piano, piano moving performed by Liberty Bell Moving offers homeowners peace of mind knowing their piano is being moved by trained piano movers.\r\n\r\nOur trained and registered Maine piano movers and piano tuners take pride in the careful disassembly padding, strapping, shipping and reassembly of your piano.\r\n\r\n<h3>Liberty Bell Moving has the experience and equipment to handle:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>moving spinet pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving console pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving player pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving studio pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving upright pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving baby grand pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving full grand pianos</li>\r\n<li>moving concert grand piano</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nIf you have us move and tune your piano, we recommend that the piano should be acclimated to the home for 3-4 weeks before scheduling a date for a piano tuning by our Registered Piano Technician.\r\n\r\n<h3>Piano Information</h3>\r\n\r\nBesides the fact that piano is heavy – it is also bulky and has an uneven distribution of weight. With that comes inertia and problems with balancing when you try to maneuver it, especially when moving the piano in a narrow passage. Professional piano movers know that the piano is extremely sensitive to a shock because it has a very delicate inner mechanism.\r\n\r\nThe iron frame, also called the “plate”, sits atop the soundboard, and serves as the primary bulwark against the force of string tension (in a modern grand the total string tension can approach 20 tons). The frame is made of cast iron and if it cracks the damage is irreparable.\r\n\r\nNo matter how much care we put into moving your piano, we always recommend having it tuned post move. Pianos are knocked out of tune very easily. If a perfect pitch is a priority, consider having our registered piano tuner bring the original sound back into your Piano.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Small Spinet piano or console piano weigh about 300-500 pounds</li>\r\n<li>Full size upright piano (also called Russian Piano) weighs about 700 pound or more</li>\r\n<li>Baby Grand piano, grand piano or parlor pianos – can weigh up to 1300 pounds</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Piano Movers','','inherit','open','open','','20-revision-5','','','2012-01-17 20:26:11','2012-01-17 20:26:11','',20,'http://libertybellmoving.com/20-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(401,1,'2012-01-17 20:26:02','2012-01-17 20:26:02','